{"type":"message","id":"631b150c","parentId":"8c60d045","timestamp":"2026-03-28T01:28:56.354Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3jyrp8blz61n_1","toolName":"sessions_list","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"count\": 1,\n  \"sessions\": [\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习\",\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774661329841,\n      \"sessionId\": \"09de5dee-8dde-477f-afa0-6b9c85d430c0\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 50759,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/09de5dee-8dde-477f-afa0-6b9c85d430c0.jsonl\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"count":1,"sessions":[{"key":"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","label":"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1774661329841,"sessionId":"09de5dee-8dde-477f-afa0-6b9c85d430c0","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":50759,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/09de5dee-8dde-477f-afa0-6b9c85d430c0.jsonl"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774661336344}}
{"type":"message","id":"415bba39","parentId":"631b150c","timestamp":"2026-03-28T01:28:59.783Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the cron job itself. This is a system session, not a user conversation. There are no active user messages in the last 5 minutes. I should execute the autonomous learning task.\n\nLet me search for the latest news on 企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务.","thinkingSignature":"3580c360b37cd0888ed835fa85f72db682f48eaa29897b4ec0df91847dabb7ee"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到只有 cron 任务自身在运行，没有用户活跃对话。执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9xn9yxr2n2f9_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":638,"output":123,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44742,"cost":{"input":0.0001914,"output":0.00014759999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0016584299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774661336353}}
{"type":"message","id":"07df517e","parentId":"415bba39","timestamp":"2026-03-28T01:28:59.790Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9xn9yxr2n2f9_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774661339787}}
{"type":"message","id":"e73f75d9","parentId":"07df517e","timestamp":"2026-03-28T01:29:03.937Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me search for relevant industry news.","thinkingSignature":"e7ac4281fa51014d11cef3ba366ef34db6e340ff91fd96838fbc9cf7cc7805ed"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3mvvfv0n82uq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型最新动态 2026\" 2>&1 | head -100","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3mvvfv0n82uq_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026\" 2>&1 | head -100","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3mvvfv0n82uq_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 行业趋势 2026\" 2>&1 | head -100","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1276,"output":184,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45441,"cost":{"input":0.0003828,"output":0.0002208,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0019230299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774661339789}}
